text: Abdul Salam Amur Juma Al-Mukhaini (7 April 1988 – 21 January 2025), commonly known as Abdul Salam Al-Mukhaini, was an Omani professional footballer who played as a centre-back. He played for the Oman national football team from 2009 until 2025, making 70 appearances.
